snippet.title: Madhouse Madness - Offical Teaser Trailer (2023) | New PC Game
snippet.description:
A journalist decides to explore an abandoned mental hospital with a dark history of housing some of the most notorious patients in history. As the journalist explores, they encounter the unique and terrifying stories of each ghost, driven by their own individual mental illnesses.

Add to Wishlist Now  -  https://store.steampowered.com/app/2358420/Madhouse_Madness/
Join Discord  -  https://discord.gg/nR3QxFas
